Name: Biomass: Aboveground
Description: Carbon in all aboveground biomass pools

Name: Biomass: Belowground
Description: Carbon in all belowground biomnass pools (coarse plus fine roots)

Name: Biomass: Total
Description: Carbon in aboverground and belowground biomass pools

Name: DOM: Aboveground
Description: Carbon in DOM pools above the mineral soil

Name: DOM: Belowground
Description: Carbon in DOM pools in the mineral soil

Name: Total Ecosystem
Description: Carbon in Biomass and DOM pools

Name: DOM: Deadwood
Description: Snag stems and branches; coarse woody debris on the ground; dead coarse roots

Name: DOM: Litter
Description: Fine and small dead woody debris; dead coarse roots in the forest floor; foliar litter; dead fine roots

Name: DOM: Soil
Description: Dead fine roots in the mineral soil; humified organic matter in the mineral soil

Name: DOM: Down Deadwood
Description: Dead coarse roots in the mineral soil; coarse woody debris on the ground
